# README.md
Slides created for presentations

```text
my-presentation/
├── slides.md               # Slidev deck
├── diagrams/               # .excalidraw source files
│   └── architecture.excalidraw
├── assets/                 # exported SVGs (git-committed)
│   └── architecture.svg
├── export.sh               # re-export all diagrams to SVG
└── CLAUDE.md               # instructions for Claude Code
```
